    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/00afffeed3de424df6f492ac7cd19e1b.avif?t=1640159600\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>尊敬的旅行者您好。<br>这是一封来自于王国的信件<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/2fce9d1cd85cd40b18cf26933841b55e.webp?t=1640159600\" width=48 height=48 /></span>，请在确认无误后查收。<br>国王听闻了您与可怕的章鱼怪物进行战斗时不幸坠入漩涡的噩耗，<br>但似乎您随着漩涡前往了王国疆域之外的海域。<br>或许您可以探索那片未知的海域传颂王国的威名！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/c0ed6f4abe58d989bc2799ed862d4484.avif?t=1640159600\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>首先，<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存下去！</h2>在游戏中，你可以<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/27bb6ed21de936df8e5063b8d84222bf.webp?t=1640159600\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>来补充体力和水分<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/8a1052d448b2bdc9dc9251a17daa0a85.webp?t=1640159600\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>来获得食物和素材<br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/30c64b27f2f8ffcd08d3f6fcf36bfc7d.webp?t=1640159600\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>当你拥有了年轻人的第一艘小船，<br>就终于可以逃离这个野蛮的小岛，回归文明社会了！<br>当然，你也可以探索更多的荒岛，当一个海上霸主！<br>准备好你的航海口粮，当你踏上远洋道路，你就可以：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/d81b3f62644ac70e269e300c012c30ca.avif?t=1640159600\" width=562 height=412 /></span><br>●探索岛屿开启更多的宝箱！<br>●在城镇完成NPC的各种委托。<br>●制作武器装备以及道具，放置物品和家具，与商人交易。<br>●扬帆起航，在海域中遭遇海盗、怪物和随机事件。（并船毁人亡<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/fccd596517604945ae0bdc19b3488874.avif?t=1640159600\" width=254 height=109 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/c6790addcc6ddf4cea6b7d07e4a28c36.webp?t=1640159600\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><strong>此外，游戏中还将包含：</strong><br>●大量的合成配方。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/a68e7e3e617a48b1cd979bcf8cd6494d.poster.avif?t=1640159600\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/a68e7e3e617a48b1cd979bcf8cd6494d.webm?t=1640159600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/a68e7e3e617a48b1cd979bcf8cd6494d.mp4?t=1640159600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>●大量的野外挨打。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/1b154efc26134a7c0ad9b8c9dc28b626.poster.avif?t=1640159600\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/1b154efc26134a7c0ad9b8c9dc28b626.webm?t=1640159600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/1b154efc26134a7c0ad9b8c9dc28b626.mp4?t=1640159600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>●以及大型BOSS战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751230/extras/55fd0a663b4e2c3b083edb2b5f36e861.poster.avif?t=1640